    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a PyGObject3 Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>PyGObject3</application> provides
<application>Python</application> bindings to the GObject class from
<application>GLib</application>.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

